snippet.title: Fate/Samurai Remnant - DLC Vol. 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Fate/Samurai Remnant DLC 3 "Record's Fragment: Bailong and the Crimson Demon" is out now!
 
In an Edo ravaged by chaos, aspirants of the Waxing Moon, together with a new Rogue Rider Zhao Yun, join forces to fight against a new foe.
